``Oyora Shrine'' is located in {{ill|lt=Osaka City|Q35765|WD=Q35765|1=Osaka}}{{ill|lt=Sumiyoshi Ward|Q985702|WD=Q985702|1=Sumiyoshi-ku, Osaka}}. {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Shikinaisha|1=Shikinaisha|WD=Q134917286}} ({{ill|lt=Meishin Taisha|Q9610964|WD=Q9610964|1=Myōjin Taisha}}) and {{ill|lt=Modern shrine rank system|Q712534|WD=Q712534|lt=Old shrine rank|1=Modern system of ranked Shinto shrines}} is {{ill|UNKNOWN|WD=Q134917326|lt=Fusha|1=Fu-sha}}. Currently, it is {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=standalone shrine|1=UNKNOWN}} which does not belong to {{ill|lt=Shinja Honcho|Q908077|WD=Q908077|1=Association of Shinto Shrines}}.

=== Enshrined God ===
The deities enshrined are as follows (the place names in parentheses are the old places before they were enshrined). </ref><ref name="Anonymous-20240629112444">[https://yosami-jinja.com/page-5741/ Oyora Shrine History]</ref>.
* Main enshrined deity
** Taketoyo Hazurawake no Kimi - 9th {{ill|lt=Kaika Emperor|Q333548|WD=Q333548|1=Emperor Kaika}}{{ill|lt=prince|Q12886381|WD=Q12886381|1=Imperial Prince}}.
** {{ill|lt=Sumiyoshi Sanjin|Q1114013|WD=Q1114013|lt=Sotsutsu no Onomikoto|1=Sumiyoshi sanjin}} - One of the pillars of {{ill|lt=Sumiyoshi Sanjin|Q1114013|WD=Q1114013|1=Sumiyoshi sanjin}}.
** {{ill|lt=Sumiyoshi Sanjin|Q1114013|WD=Q1114013|lt=Nakatsutsuno no Mikoto|1=Sumiyoshi sanjin}} (Nakatsutsu no Mikoto) - One of the pillars of the Sumiyoshi Sanjin.
** {{ill|lt=Sumiyoshi Sanjin|Q1114013|WD=Q1114013|lt=Uwatsutsu no Omikoto|1=Sumiyoshi sanjin}} (Uwatsutsu no Onomikoto) - One of the three Sumiyoshi Gods<ref>On the homepage of Oyora Shrine, it is listed as Omotzutsu no Omikoto. </ref>.

* Deity enshrined
** {{ill|WD=Q276944|lt=Okuninushi|Q276944|WD=Q276944|lt=Takamiko Omi|1=Ōkuninushi}}, {{ill|WD=Q595520|lt=Tsukuyomi|Q595520|WD=Q595520|WD=Q595520|lt=Tsukuyomi no Mikoto|1=Tsukuyomi-no-Mikoto}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Emperor Suinin|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|lt=Goju Takekami|Q10881556|WD=Q10881556|lt=Goju Takekami|1=Isotakeru-no-Mikoto}}, (Kushimeigyoku no Mikoto<ref>It is listed as a deity enshrined on the home page of Oyora Shrine.</ref>)

